Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:53.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&H838383&,&H838383&)}在内心深处定居的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:57.14,OP,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&H838383&,&H838383&)}{\t(3396,3563,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&)}成群魔物即将苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:03.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&H838383&,&H838383&)}{\fad(200,0)}向邪恶挥舞复仇之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:07.19,OP,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&H838383&,&H838383&)}为善良赐予救济之死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:10.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&H838383&,&H838383&)}{\fad(0,200)}我这污秽的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:13.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&H838383&,&H838383&)}究竟会斩向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:14.86,OP,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&H838383&,&H838383&)}{\fad(0,300)}挺身而出
